ChangeLog for aic8800-sdk

2025-02-12 - v6.6.0.1
  * aic8800 update
    - wifi fmacfw_api.c
  * aic8800mc update
    - dcdc vrf driver capa enhance during sleep mode
  * aic8800m40 update
    - support wifi dynamic dpd cal process, cal res can be stored in flash
    - add target_wifi_p2p & target_wifi_p2p_fhosti
  * wifi update
    - set default ps keep alive time to 60s
    - wlan_start_sta add password mismatch check
    - fix mem leak
    - support P2P go
  * btdm update
    - ble add set bt addr process for user
    - u04 patch
    - open GAPC_TK_EXCH case
    - ble add get rssi cmd in console
  * fhostif update
    - add show_hostif_user_filter
    - target_*_nocopy fix MCU & HOST shared pkt bug
  * rtos update
    - fault handler print, add crash log parser
    - rtos_task_info support called in isr context

